18:
However, those wicked people will disappear very quickly,\q2 and God will curse the land that they owned;
\q2 no one will go any longer to work in their vineyards.
\q1

24:
They prosper for a little while,\q2 and then suddenly they are gone;
\q2 God will make them die like all the other people;
\q2 they will be like stalks of grain that the farmers have cut off.
\q1
